# Data Pipeline

This pipeline supports two datasets:
- Fake/True news articles (article-level classification)
- LIAR claims (claim-level truthfulness benchmark)

## LIAR mapping rules

- REAL: `true`, `mostly-true`, `half-true`
- FAKE: `barely-true`, `false`, `pants-fire`
- Input text: statement only (speaker/party/history removed)

## Processing steps

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  A[Raw Data] --> B[Load + Parse]
  B --> C[Normalize Schema]
  C --> D[Clean Text\nlowercase, strip URLs/emails, whitespace]
  D --> E[Build Clean Columns\nbody_clean, title_clean, combined_clean]
  E --> F[Train/Test Split\nFake/True]
  E --> G[Official Splits\nLIAR train/valid/test]
```
